descriptionHtml:
Interactive Skyrim

skyrim 1.8.151 and latest SKSE required

This mod allows the player to use certain animation which is used by other npcs in game
like warm hands near fire,dance during the bards singing the songs,farming in farm,feeding
the chickens and many other animation markers such as that other npcs uses in game.

To activate the animation stand near the objects and press insert button the animations will 
start automatically according to the objects which you are standing near.

To stop the animation Press Delete button.
author: Praveen
